// 2. Space complexity: BST uses O(n) extra space vs Selection Sort O(1)
// 3. No balancing: BST can become skewed
// 4. Inefficient approach: Sorting then building BST is unnecessary

// Running time analysis:
// Selection Sort: O(n²) time, O(1) space
// BST construction: O(n²) worst case, O(n log n) average case
// Combined: O(n²) overall

